Notes:
Houses a collection of artifacts, photographs, documents and other materials related to the history of Lake Mary and the surrounding communities. Lots of old helmets, uniforms, models, magazines, papers and other memorablia that represents the military, especially Lake Mary's contribution to the various wars.The building was built in 1926 and is on the National Registry of Historical Places
 It is run by the Lake Mary Historical Society which also has their meetings at the facilty
